{"tid":1076520,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【《尋秦記》電影版】陶總管另有人選？ 歐瑞偉：根本冇聯絡我","createTime":"2019-03-25T02:05:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-25T09:59:27.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"4d7f8a539a03caabfb60fe5e42ed7bae6d41a3ef","tid":1076520,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T02:05:30.000Z","msg":"《尋秦記》開拍電影版，古天樂日前出席影視博覽時，與幾位「舊情人」再見面，連秦始皇林峯都有出席，當日古天樂提到很難得可以再與電視版原班人馬合作，不過台上少了項少龍身邊的陶總管&mdash;&mdash;歐瑞偉。<br />\n歐瑞偉今日於九龍灣出席活動，染了一頭灰白頭髮，造型酷似財政司司長陳茂波，他說除了《愛。回家》，又正為TVB劇拍新劇，故要keep住造型出席。講到《尋秦記》電影版，歐瑞偉透露原來沒有收過演出邀請：「根本冇聯絡過我，可能係拍呢一邊故事啦。」他又大感可惜：「都可惜㗎，不過隨緣啦，畢竟都係經典嘅製作，我都想參與，要顧及好多因素。」<br />\n另外，馬德鐘今日為活動擔任頒獎嘉賓，他承認成為視帝後多了商演活動參與。提到近況，馬德鐘表示近日影響了好友陳山聰食素，他說：「佢話見到我好似回咗春咁，山聰跟我食咗素一個月，覺得呢個飲食習慣好好，又可以影響到身邊嘅人。之前一班朋友有時出嚟聚會，就會佢有佢哋食，我有我食素，但而家影響到其他人，覺得好好。」山聰亦指：「係呀，我覺得佢真係回咗春，我就回緊。」<br />\n山聰接着說：「近幾個月食全素，之前玩gym食得太多肉，而家食素覺得OK。（喺香港食素會唔會覺得唔方便？）咁又唔係，其實都好普及，好多地方都有，食咗素之後覺得自己精神咗，磅數亦速跌，好快就跌咗8磅，自己照樣食飯、意粉等澱粉質食物，但冇食肉。」正在開劇的山聰表示，由於同劇演員姚子羚也是素食者，而且食素年資很長，所以今次轉為素食者後最大得着是姚子羚會煲素湯返去給他一起飲，而山聰的女朋友有時都會煲素菜湯，他們就可以互相分享。山聰覺得食素之後精神好好，現時每天都只是睡幾小時，就算戲裏面有動作打戲，自己都完全應付到，他和馬德鐘希望未來可以有合作，因為兩人對上一次都已經是10年前的事。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190324/large/1553425493_56c5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190324%2Flarge%2F1553425493_56c5.jpg&h=ae6454f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190324/large/1553425493_de95.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190324%2Flarge%2F1553425493_de95.jpg&h=a20ba0b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190324/large/1553425494_e678.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190324%2Flarge%2F1553425494_e678.jpg&h=1f128a27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190324/large/1553425495_fc79.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190324%2Flarge%2F1553425495_fc79.jpg&h=c8f17831&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190324/large/1553425495_ed17.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190324%2Flarge%2F1553425495_ed17.jpg&h=d55f6ef1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190324/59406876\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190324%2F59406876&d=Peq93FhG%2BXbpjcIFBj2O6aCH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=72bf7fae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190324%2F59406876&h=19f64dcd\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190324/59406876</a>"},{"pid":"b1abc7b3714fd0c118d023af97b39c2536b495d6","tid":1076520,"uid":22913,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T02:12:06.000Z","msg":"八婆"},{"pid":"5ba1eb6b19e61376f86be85712f014df1e55500e","tid":1076520,"uid":7206,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T04:15:42.000Z","msg":"可能搵大陸佬做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />合拍片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19e78d619b1fca8001eea613a57620ace588f3e2","tid":1076520,"uid":34553,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T04:22:09.000Z","msg":"除非冇陶總管呢個角色<br />\n如果唔係都幾仆街"},{"pid":"492572cc904edf31e1c893a0bf53d7b72bd63c06","tid":1076520,"uid":5652,"like":11,"dislike":20,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"19e78d619b1fca8001eea613a57620ace588f3e2","tid":1076520,"uid":34553,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T04:22:09.000Z","msg":"